text: Aytugan () is a rural locality (a selo) in Yasherganovsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 203 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Sterlibashevo, 5 km from Yasherganovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Aytugan, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
